{"tid":1848143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假封關後。所有大陸人會集中曬係東鐵綫口岸，深圳灣","createTime":"2020-01-28T10:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:45:37.000Z","uid":217430,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fd21d3267ce30ca74a66348566b8fcbb8db540","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhOV1zx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhOV1zx.jpg&h=8ba131f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvb8Ccz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhvb8Ccz.jpg&h=8b1852ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最多人用既關口唔封。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n東鐵綫同深圳灣將會車水馬龍。<br />\n<br />\n呢家先停止自由行簽證審批係無用的。有好多大陸人一早有自由行簽證。<br />\n而且，除左自由行簽證。重有好多鍾類簽證可以申請，並將會成為漏洞：<span style=\"color: red;\">團體、商務、探親</span>。<br />\n呢幾種簽證都係好容易申請倒的。<br />\n<br />\n結論係<br />\n<br />\n完全無封過關，反而重要將所有支那人迫曬去同東鐵線接壤嘅落馬洲支線、羅湖口岸，同埋深圳灣。"},{"pid":"0f4c16453a2b1261f024bad6bf5a6a48431a3be2","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45fb17771f516f439cafc68323ce3ec91b510d9e","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:16:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a319ce5976e22c03f9149c6e64c97e75e422b730","tid":1848143,"uid":132217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:16:34.000Z","msg":"點解只係得醫護叫罷工，去晒一兩個關口，海關的人唔係仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁死於人禍之下值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n海關自行封關啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無人救到你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ed007afeaedfd04f2cd64e7b21fd76be2d59a","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb59e8d4c1ba5e1d9290e56606896c27b309b743","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"440e8151d01500209069b0224ac2d9b7e61eb822","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:16:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"851a26e98b0ce463b1e6b840521b94124877aa92","tid":1848143,"uid":132217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"推到海關見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07d8e0be855b54d1fbd778b20e6be1ec1adde8c","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"係重未真封關前<br />\n大家先萬唔好坐東鐵<br />\n好撚早危"},{"pid":"7a7f8a6a61357263093d88d2ffa1c1920f063d55","tid":1848143,"uid":217430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係重未真封關前<br />\n大家先萬唔好坐東鐵<br />\n好撚高危</blockquote>"},{"pid":"9db8ef26c584d804eca72ab046f644e309c6b404","tid":1848143,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJLpUGP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJLpUGP.gif&h=9b7754dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89423fb742654581ee5673a0e39652bb37e9c5a6","tid":1848143,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T10:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19667897c69e933e4b4d2803b59b464b6b6350b","tid":1848143,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"851a26e98b0ce463b1e6b840521b94124877aa92",